## Key Determinism Note

Baseline unanimity (test-retest on baseline prompts):

- Gemini: `71.2%` (temp 0.2) -> `87.2%` (temp 0.0)
- GPT-5.4: `94.8%` (temp 0.2) -> `96.4%` (temp 0.0)

Interpretation: temp-0 improved baseline repeatability for both models but did not produce perfect (`100%`) determinism.

